{"tid":1537142,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平強調：凡是危害國家安全 須堅決鬥爭","createTime":"2019-09-03T22:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T04:43:35.000Z","uid":187112,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2764892b90279fe715f5b21a7f1a9fcab33cf44a","tid":1537142,"uid":187112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T22:51:19.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3KVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=e747298a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】中國國家主席習近平周二（3日）上午出席中央黨校（國家行政學院）中青年幹部培訓班的開班儀式，他發表講話時，提及港澳台面臨重大鬥爭，強調凡是危害中共領導和中國社會主義制度、危害國家主權、安全、危害國家核心利益和重大原則、危害人民根本利益等各種風險挑戰，就必須堅決鬥爭，並取得勝利。另籲市民頭腦清醒、立場堅定，把握正確鬥爭的方向，在重大鬥爭考驗面前「不畏浮雲遮望眼」，「亂雲飛渡仍從容」。<br />\n<br />\n習近平指出，中國當前發展至進入各種風險挑戰不斷積累，甚至集中顯露的時期，面臨愈來愈複雜的不少重大鬥爭，包括經濟、政治、文化、社會、國防和軍隊建設、港澳台工作、外交工作等方面。而領導及幹部需預判潛在風險及其發展趨勢，該鬥爭時就要鬥爭。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，在各種重大鬥爭中，要堅持增強憂患意識、保持戰略定力及判斷、鬥爭過程及實效相統一。在抓住鬥爭上的主要矛盾，堅持有理有利有節，合理選擇鬥爭方式，在原則問題上寸步不讓。另根據形勢需要，調整鬥爭策略，團結一切力量，爭取、謀求合作獲得共贏。<br />\n<br />\n習又強調，鬥爭的精神及本領，並不是與生俱來。領導、幹部要在複雜嚴峻的鬥爭中，受嚴格思想淬煉、政治歷練；主動投身到各種鬥爭，在大是大非面前敢於亮劍，在矛盾衝突面前敢於迎難而上，在危機困難面前敢於挺身而出，在歪風邪氣面前敢於堅決鬥爭。<br />\n<br />\n他又形容社會是在矛盾運動中前進的，有矛盾就會有鬥爭。幹部應不論崗位、職務，全面從嚴治黨、堅持馬克思主義在意識形態領域的指導地位，又強調要消除金融領域隱患、保障和改善民生、打贏脫貧攻堅戰、應對重大自然災害、全面依法治國、處理群體性事件、打擊黑惡勢力、維護國家安全等。並呼籲領導幹部都要敢於、善於鬥爭的戰士。<br />\n<br />\n階級鬥爭來了。"},{"pid":"02cf927aa89af62212137d2f254bc4b3c0c3b32c","tid":1537142,"uid":60434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T22:52:20.000Z","msg":"習近平<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zfkb65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zfkb65.jpg&h=778f49e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3ddf801a0e3d17a73fd31d4042c1878d148a512","tid":1537142,"uid":187112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02cf927aa89af62212137d2f254bc4b3c0c3b32c","tid":1537142,"uid":60434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T22:52:20.000Z","msg":"習近平<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zfkb65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zfkb65.jpg&h=778f49e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T22:55:42.000Z","msg":"玩階級鬥爭。內裡搞文革，外交上撐獨裁，孤立自己"},{"pid":"eb4771e5af955aae6f46b055bb889b8de2c7b7ea","tid":1537142,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T22:58:43.000Z","msg":"我每個post 都會咒一次：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警全家變植物人</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">(集中討論) <br />\n908 九月八日 2:00pm <br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》集會請願 ! ! <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">扯國旗!</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">唱國歌 !</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536086\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kCGOYms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCGOYms.jpg&h=ced74507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/JGPEpwY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGPEpwY.jpg&h=115c89d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽歌隨意門(附歌詞):</span></span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3KVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=7429bd5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">手足動人獻唱自由國度之歌</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNfTjAM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNfTjAM.gif&h=db1663f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3KVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=d5d1e905\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a>"},{"pid":"14f0a7184e7dbfdbea8a9309eb8d4771ed4afd40","tid":1537142,"uid":35457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:02:09.000Z","msg":"佢無架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9dffa6e3d20dca92f7c8a26d53c7b2d6012955","tid":1537142,"uid":32221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:02:35.000Z","msg":"啲人仲想幫佢洗白話唔關佢事<br />\n跟本條撚樣就係始作俑者"},{"pid":"6bcab38434b916ddfe0b082bf6fdb6c237420560","tid":1537142,"uid":217450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:03:46.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"2ec44f94d811ee708c34955cabe7e106f8bb75d4","tid":1537142,"uid":187112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14f0a7184e7dbfdbea8a9309eb8d4771ed4afd40","tid":1537142,"uid":35457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:02:09.000Z","msg":"佢無架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:04:40.000Z","msg":"個腦壞左"},{"pid":"d06d3ca83037772247e8e417048ac79b3a7533c7","tid":1537142,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:05:08.000Z","msg":"嚟喇嚟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n紅衛兵！紅衛兵！"},{"pid":"8dada724ffb380da24ac650aee302cedef387db1","tid":1537142,"uid":187112,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6bcab38434b9